text:
Great food. A restaurant like this is sorely needed. Only drawback is that the hightop tables are too small! Everything on it is too crowded and I feel like something’s going to fall off.

////////
Update Apr. 2021 — I really wish there was a section on the website of *just* the menu. I don’t want to have to download door dash, log in and almost place an order all just to see what’s on the dang menu. Photos of menus on Google aren’t always up to date.
